{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2944 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2944 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2944","pos":[618,638]},{"content":"'class' : type-class-id redefined as a value argument of a template","pos":[639,706]},{"content":"You cannot use a generic or template class, instead of a symbol, as a template value argument.","pos":[713,807]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2944:","pos":[814,851]},{"content":"C2944 can also occur when using generics:","pos":[1041,1082]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2944 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2944\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2944\"\nms.assetid: f209e668-e72f-442a-a438-8c4ff43a404a\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2944\n'class' : type-class-id redefined as a value argument of a template  \n  \n You cannot use a generic or template class, instead of a symbol, as a template value argument.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2944:  \n  \n```  \n// C2944.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \ntemplate<class T>  \nclass TC { };   \n  \ntemplate <int TC<int> > struct X1 { };   // C2944  \n  \ntemplate <class T > struct X2 {};  \n```  \n  \n C2944 can also occur when using generics:  \n  \n```  \n// C2944b.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr /c  \ngeneric<class T>  \nref class GC {};  \n  \ntemplate <int GC<int> > struct X2 { };   // C2944  \ntemplate <class T> struct X3 {};   // OK  \n```"}